## ‚ú® Features

- ü§ñ **AI-Powered Commit Messages:** Automatically generates meaningful and conventional commit messages based on code changes, saving time and ensuring consistency;
- üõ†Ô∏è **Repository Management:** Provides tools to manage repository descriptions, README files, and topics with AI assistance, making repository maintenance effortless;
- üöÄ **Quick Setup:** Easy to install and configure, with a simple CLI interface that integrates seamlessly into your development workflow;
- üìö **Documentation Generation:** Automatically generates help documentation and README sections, ensuring your project is well-documented and easy to understand;
- üîÑ **Git Integration:** Deep integration with Git, allowing you to manage commits, repositories, and GitHub interactions directly from the CLI;
- üß† **Customizable Prompts:** Supports custom prompt templates for generating commit messages, descriptions, and other content, tailored to your project's needs;
- üåê **GitHub API Integration:** Seamlessly interacts with GitHub to update repository descriptions and topics, ensuring your project is always up-to-date;
- üì¶ **Modular Design:** Built with a modular architecture, allowing you to extend and customize functionality to fit your specific requirements;

